    "body": "### Describe your issue\n\nI'm wondering if it's worth delaying decrefs until after a `critical_section` (to minimize the amount of unseen arbitrary code that can interrupt them).\n\nThis would obvious only apply to things directly inside the scope of a critical section (rather than any functions that they call).\n\nI'm not yet sure how much this would complicate code generation, and how practically useful it'd be. So at the moment I'm only writing it down for future consideration.",
